Package uk.co.kring.kodek

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BitStack
    A bit stack implemented with coding on a generator set.
    Block
    A data block to place on the block stack.
    BlockInputStream
    A stream to read blocks from.
    BlockOutputStream
    A steam to write output written blocks.
    BlockStack
    A stack to place blocks on implemented using a bit stack and having an important property of also being a block on the stack as well as the stack container.
    BlockStore
    A key base store which uses a kodek to store data.
    BlockTree
    A tree structure to allow addressing speed.
    Chaos
    A reversible pseudo random bit generator.
    Generator
    A bit bias generator using PQ asymmetry sequencing.
    GenSet
    A set of generators to make a critical bias for storage.
